l/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n學位貶值係香港主要唔係學位太多 我自己覺得<br />\n而係香港社會結構已經有問題<br />\n加上學生愈黎愈少 令入到u既學生質素下降<br />\n佢升唔升大學都係開緊degree programme啦 升左都係掛個名 不如你去屌asso仲好<br />\n出到國外同人講你asso會比人笑<br />\n我諗你咁關注恒大升唔升到既有 不如focus返其他令學位貶值既主因"},{"pid":"e738792e73fbbab6ef24d1fbce92191504a9eacf","tid":390704,"uid":66597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T09:46:50.000Z","msg":"收皮啦 年年都煲話申請緊 講撚左咁多年都無進展<br />\n都唔知係咪專登昆人讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26f8b6a3d0596e2407f2ae7627e9fafa55d22f91","tid":390704,"uid":62167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T09:53:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>痕大升唔到 應該就無下一間大學架啦香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港咁撚細要咁多大學做咩<br />\n嫌學位貶值得唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n學位貶值係香港主要唔係學位太多 我自己覺得<br />\n而係香港社會結構已經有問題<br />\n加上學生愈黎愈少 令入到u既學生質素下降<br />\n佢升唔升大學都係開緊degree programme啦 升左都係掛個名 不如你去屌asso仲好<br />\n出到國外同人講你asso會比人笑<br />\n我諗你咁關注恒大升唔升到既有 不如focus返其他令學位貶值既主因</blockquote><br />\n其實香港冇幾多工作係真正需要degree holder ,不過一街大學生（計埋自資）所以先加個門檻落去。<br />\n說穿了香港大部分人都係做sales<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec356f8fa14b8d14429028de8d217df5d022073d","tid":390704,"uid":45657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T09:55:44.000Z","msg":"原來有咁多痕大支持者 失覺晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f598bc3c4bc2793b6cee1259e298cea4514b4f05","tid":390704,"uid":25552,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T10:18:04.000Z","msg":"咁幾時到Ive<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27ef8caf22094ee03b4ad96f7384ce2